# Stanzix Project Rules

## What is Stanzix

Stanzix is a structured prompt builder. Users describe what they need, configure 8 levers (Tone, Depth, Format, Role, Audience, Output, Constraints, Examples), and get a structured prompt ready to paste into any LLM.

This codebase is the MARKETING WEBSITE at stanzix.com. The product app lives separately at app.stanzix.com.

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript (strict mode)
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion (light use only)
- next/font for Geist, Geist Mono, Fraunces
- Vercel Analytics
- Deployed to Vercel

Do not introduce additional dependencies without justification.

## Design Tokens (use these literally)

### Colors
- background: `#0A0A0A` (warm black, not pure)
- surface: `#141414`
- text-primary: `#F5F1E8` (cream white)
- text-secondary: `#8B8579` (warm muted)
- text-dim: `#5C564D`
- accent: `#D4A04C` (amber - the Stanzix signature)
- accent-hover: `#C49340`
- accent-dim: `#8B6B30`
- border: `#2A2620`
