### Typography
- Headlines: Fraunces (font-serif). Weights 400-600. Use `font-medium` for h1-h3.
- Body: Geist (font-sans). Weights 400-500.
- Code/Mono: Geist Mono (font-mono).

### Type Scale
- Display (h1): `font-serif text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-[1.05]`
- H2: `font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium tracking-tight`
- H3: `font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium`
- Body Large: `font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed`
- Body: `font-sans text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed`
- Caption: `font-sans text-sm text-text-dim uppercase tracking-wider`
- Code: `font-mono text-sm md:text-base`

### Spacing
- Section padding: `py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40`
- Container: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12`
